      "side": 1,
      "message": "At one point I said it wouldn\u0027t be a good idea to store Job IDs in Task, but now I think I was wrong. My reasoning was that if a new Job is manually triggered, the existing Tasks wouldn\u0027t point to that Job; however, I think that\u0027s actually a feature, not a bug, since we want to trigger new Tasks for a manually-triggered Job. We can talk more if that doesn\u0027t make sense.",
